{"tid":1692553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"11月24號投票一定要朝早一開就排隊","createTime":"2019-11-04T06:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T16:39:27.000Z","uid":273374,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ed40582d391f5a9c927c7d6454fec87c82faaabd","tid":1692553,"uid":273374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:35:32.000Z","msg":"今次投票一定要朝早一開就排隊。政府無暫停區選, 一定有方法影響選舉結果。<br />\n1. 有機會提早cut vote<br />\n2. 後生通常最last minute投, 差佬有機會下午tg搞到無人投倒票。<br />\n<br />\n七點半開始投票，大家果日一定要一開始就落去等(七點)，搞到幾百/上千人排隊，一來可以增加氣勢，二來增加藍絲公公婆婆投共的成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做倒既盡力做。雖然唔知會唔會果日最尾取消。但planning好重要。如果有新idea就再加。"},{"pid":"06f73f724cec2e7d342b0d4d682305c6a6ee7cea","tid":1692553,"uid":88870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5fc5a4bffad0b3dd3626807ed1b7401aa498c060","tid":1692553,"uid":6384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:26:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eea51c2b4b319d68f3a19c9ec5b94db798e7963","tid":1692553,"uid":111493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:28:09.000Z","msg":"推 照計會晨早幾車阿公阿婆大陸人去投<br />\n一到下午就話人太多有搞事分女要提早cut vote<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n劇本  所以大家醒定早投有so"},{"pid":"a8297d5675e819e2b70742a691933ccb09c0d760","tid":1692553,"uid":6316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:30:24.000Z","msg":"大家可以盡孝心請家人去旅行, day trip都得"},{"pid":"20494854fa7314819e2cc14b6d3d03c84617e66f","tid